snippet.title: THUMPER Rhythm Violence Teaser
snippet.description:
Thumper is a rhythm violence game.  It combines classic rhythm-action with speed and physicality.  
For the latest development news: http://drool.ws.
NOTE: trailer contains alpha gameplay footage.  Nothing is final quality.
